SIMPLE: sea_legs
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sea legs
<hw>Sea" legs`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>Legs able to maintain their
possessor upright in stormy weather at sea, that is, ability to stand or
walk steadily on deck when a vessel is rolling or pitching in a rough
sea.</def> <mark>[Sailor's Cant]</mark> <rj><au>Totten.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sea lemon</ent>⟦br⟧
